    <item>
      <title>因债务纠纷，俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司将停止向摩尔多瓦供应天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/gazprom-to-halt-gas-supply-to-moldova-on-debt-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于东欧国家摩尔多瓦能源部门进入紧急状态，俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 涉嫌陷入债务僵局，将从 1 月 1 日起停止向摩尔多瓦供应天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/gazprom-to-halt-gas-supply-to-moldova-on-debt-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔的 Sonko 绕过议会通过 2025 年预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/senegal-s-sonko-bypasses-parliament-to-adopt-2025-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总理奥斯曼·松科（Ousmane Sonko）批准了明年的预算，绕过了议会对 6.4 万亿非洲金融共同体法郎（102 亿美元）一揽子计划的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/senegal-s-sonko-bypasses-parliament-to-adopt-2025-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:07:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行希望分得 Tether 数十亿美元的稳定币利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/banks-want-in-on-tether-s-billions-in-stablecoin-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直到最近，银行还在羡慕地旁观稳定币市场领导者 Tether Holdings 吹嘘其利润达数十亿美元。现在他们也想加入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/banks-want-in-on-tether-s-billions-in-stablecoin-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安称土耳其利率将在 2025 年下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/erdogan-says-turkey-interest-rates-will-definitely-fall-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安表示，2025年利率将会下降，他再次表达了自己非传统的信念，即降低利率将减缓物价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/erdogan-says-turkey-interest-rates-will-definitely-fall-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 13:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
